**What this fixes:**
1. **Real machine code emission** – No more stub failure; emits actual x64 opcodes (REX prefixes, ModR/M, etc.)
2. **Valid PE32+ headers** – Generates Windows-native 64-bit executables (not just .obj files)
3. **Instruction encoder** – Supports `mov r64,imm64`, `add r64,r64`, `push`/`pop`, `ret`, `nop`, `syscall`
4. **Alignment handling** – Proper SectionAlignment (0x1000) and FileAlignment (0x200) per PE spec

